snippet.title: Netlooter Trailer
snippet.description:
You are a net looter. Your ultimate goal is to steal the almighty and powerful Nethack from NotAnEvil Corporation. This Nethack can affect time and space themself. Ever dream of stopping bullets with your finger 👆?


Available now :
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.PhamThomas.NetLooter
